I'm not sure which years exactly, buy my 79 has a wire that goes to
the door buzzer that is only live when the key has been inserted into
the ignition. (not turned just inserted) With a simple use of a 12v
relay voila you don't even have to turn it, just put the key in and
tunes come forth.
